thread.title: Terry “ghostrider” rider

author: Terry “ghostrider” rider
title: Terry “ghostrider” rider
text: I had My Choice install office on my PC and they were very professional and worked with me during the complete install making certain I understood the install upon completion asked thee was anything else they could help with i.e. placing things on the desktop I asked if they could place a couple on the task bar and without hesitation I looked down and they were there. They a outstanding people to work with. GREAT JOB
